{"tid":1217022,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢兩日唔使出 咁咪冇嘢做？","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:10:19.000Z","uid":164313,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40d2ae22e27962866eadb9fa8d31a0e8afc3baaa","tid":1217022,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"你咁諗就錯<br />\n勇武要好好休息 養精蓄銳<br />\n大家都係慣咗和平嘅香港人 你話唔攰？<br />\n我就唔信<br />\n總之 休息好先可以繼續！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物資<br />\n要繼續努力收集<br />\n冇人知下次會用幾多 夠唔夠用<br />\n預多好過預少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐵膠派<br />\n明日請繼續支持地鐵<br />\n千！萬！不！要！又搞到蝕唔知幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非<br />\n請努力做好市民嘅工作<br />\n樓下有車亂泊咩？支持報警<br />\n樓上好似家庭暴力喎？支持報警<br />\n行街見到有人好似想打交咁濟？支持報警<br />\n警察責任係守護市民性命財產 解決糾紛<br />\n真係唔好報假案 你知啦<br />\n當需要警察出動 佢哋個個踩足唔知幾個鐘嘅更<br />\n又攰 點守護市民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍵盤戰士<br />\n有好嘢睇 記得繼續backup<br />\n宣揚開去 揚威國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada4c8ecec981de5291d8e7e65d744aa4a055b46","tid":1217022,"uid":164313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"學生方面<br />\n有熱忱嘅心之餘<br />\n記得要兼顧學業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩讀書冇用嗰啲<br />\n大個咪要做狗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ecd11d688cb3948920b9dd5bfbb9186b61138e","tid":1217022,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01432757bf9fc3e054b885061b05ce19064abd45","tid":1217022,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"必睇"},{"pid":"de4503063b35d91def89c40eae8c236ccb83596a","tid":1217022,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s